      "writtenOn": "2018-05-17T21:59:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "you probably need to transactionally delete all Notifier entities AND root Project entity itself, otherwise you\u0027ll be getting \"deleting notifiers for %s because the project no longer exists\" in the logs forever (nothing deletes Project entity).\n\nSo, two steps:\n1. Discover all projects needs to be delete.\n2. For each project, run a transaction that queries all entities under the project root and deletes them.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 151,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 152,
        "endChar": 58
      },
      "revId": "f7301d8c5c9e27856c1762709e7f6243ef248529",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "a32b2dfb_86a1dbca",
        "filename": "luci_notify/config/config.go",
        "patchSetId": 4
      },
      "lineNbr": 180,
